    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. The exterior shows significant wear, including several deep scratches, noticeable dents on the passenger side, and some areas of surface rust. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with tears in the seats and a non-functional air conditioning system. While the engine does start, it runs roughly and will require immediate mechanical attention or a complete overhaul to be roadworthy. This car is best suited for a dedicated project restorer or as a source for parts.",
